question: What are the most common addresses used by entities?
cypher:

RETURN a.address, COUNT(e) AS entity_count
ORDER BY entity_count DESC

question: Provide the names of entities that have a struck off date similar to 'HOTFOCUS CO., LTD.'
cypher:
// First, find the struck off date of the entity 'HOTFOCUS CO., LTD.'

WITH e1.struck_off_date AS target_struck_off_date

// Then, find other entities with the same struck off date
MATCH (e2:Entity)

question: What are the details of entities that have an incorporation date in 2006?
cypher:
MATCH (e:Entity)
WHERE e.incorporation_date CONTAINS '2006'
RETURN e.name AS entity_name, e.countries AS countries, e.ibcRUC AS ibcRUC, e.valid_until AS valid_until, 
       e.country_codes AS country_codes, e.service_provider AS service_provider, e.address AS address, 
       e.inactivation_date AS inactivation_date, e.struck_off_date AS struck_off_date, e.status AS status, 
       e.jurisdiction_description AS jurisdiction_description, e.incorporation_date AS incorporation_date, 
       e.original_name AS original_name, e.jurisdiction AS jurisdiction, e.internal_id AS internal_id, 
       e.lastEditTimestamp AS lastEditTimestamp, e.node_id AS node_id, e.sourceID AS sourceID, 
       e.former_name AS former_name, e.company_type AS company_type, e.tax_stat_description AS tax_stat_description, 
       e.note AS note, e.dorm_date AS dorm_date, e.type AS type, e.closed_date AS closed_date, 
       e.company_number AS company_number, e.comments AS comments, e.entity_number AS entity_number
typeql:
match 
$e isa offshore_entity, has incorporation_date $inc_date;
$inc_date >= 2006-01-01;
$inc_date <= 2006-12-31;
fetch {
  "entity_name": $e.name,
  "countries": $e.countries,
  "ibcRUC": $e.ibc_ruc,
  "valid_until": $e.valid_until,
  "country_codes": $e.country_codes,
  "service_provider": $e.service_provider,
  "address": $e.address,
  "inactivation_date": $e.inactivation_date,
  "struck_off_date": $e.struck_off_date,
  "status": $e.status,
  "jurisdiction_description": $e.jurisdiction_description,
  "incorporation_date": $inc_date,
  "original_name": $e.original_name,
  "jurisdiction": $e.jurisdiction,
  "internal_id": $e.internal_id,
  "lastEditTimestamp": $e.last_edit_timestamp,
  "node_id": $e.node_id,
  "sourceID": $e.source_id,
  "former_name": $e.former_name,
  "company_type": $e.company_type,
  "tax_stat_description": $e.tax_stat_description,
  "note": $e.note,
  "dorm_date": $e.dorm_date,
  "type": $e.entity_type,
  "closed_date": $e.closed_date,
  "company_number": $e.company_number,
  "comments": $e.comments,
  "entity_number": $e.entity_number
};

MATCH (o:Officer {icij_id: 'CB195B5424E13A74A6F3BC719050A2B9'})-[:connected_to]->(e:Entity)
RETURN e.name AS entity_name, e.node_id AS entity_node_id

question: Who are the officers with the former name 'MOSSFON SUBSCRIBERS LTD.' and their current names?
cypher:

RETURN o.name AS current_name, e.former_name AS former_name

question: List all intermediaries that have been registered at more than one address.
cypher:
MATCH (i:Intermediary)-[:registered_address]->(a:Address)
WITH i, COUNT(DISTINCT a) AS addressCount
WHERE addressCount > 1
RETURN i.name AS IntermediaryName, addressCount

question: Which officers are connected to entities with a struck off date of '15-FEB-2013'?

question: Identify entities that share the same company number and list their names.

question: List all addresses that have been registered to more than one entity.

MATCH (e1:Entity)-[:registered_address]->(a:Address)<-[:registered_address]-(e2:Entity)
WHERE e1.node_id <> e2.node_id
RETURN a.address AS Address, COUNT(DISTINCT e1.node_id) AS EntityCount
ORDER BY EntityCount DESC

question: List the addresses that are registered to more than one entity.

RETURN e2.name AS EntityName, e2.lastEditTimestamp AS LastEditTimestamp
